3.2.2. Application of a radial scaling to the reference model
"The second option is to apply a radial scaling of the 1D CMFGEN
model and use the same density, opacity, and emissivities as the
1D CMFGEN model on that scaled grid. For example, the den-
sity (as well as opacities and emissivities) at r along β corre-
