ing (Section 3.2.2) of a 1D CMFGEN model. In the subsequent
section, we use the combination of two models (Section 3.2.3)
and compare to all observed epochs of SN 2012aw (Section 4).
For clarity, we call these models the scaled model, the stretched
model, and the hybrid model."
"Throughout this section, we present multipanel figures that
have the same structure. The top panel shows the total flux FI
